values.content:
=Write a welcome email HTML body for a student who just set up their semester study plan. Make it warm, exciting, and practical.

Student: {{ $json.student_name }}
Course: {{ $json.course_name }}
Semester Start: {{ $json.semester_start }}
Total Weeks: 15
Week 1 Theme: {{ $json.first_week.week_theme }}
Week 1 Topics: {{ $json.first_week.topics.join(', ') }}

Include:
1. Warm welcome from StudyBuddy
2. What their plan covers (brief)
3. What to expect Week 1
4. A motivational sign-off
5. Reminder that they'll get weekly prep emails every Sunday

Use inline CSS for styling. Make it mobile-friendly. Use a clean, modern layout with a colored header. Keep it under 400 words.

